commit message:
Fixed task 20: Text not displayed 'Select Account' pop-up with
light theme
http://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/issues/issue/20

Merge pull request #22 from kvnco/french_translation

added french translation

Fixed - task 15: Status.net terminology should be used
https://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/issues/15
Fixed - task 13: Add Combined Timeline
http://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/issues/issue/13

Fixed bug: position in the timeline was not stored and widget counters
were not cleared when exiting with Back button.
Fixed FC on exiting from timeline while loading more messages
Refactored internal names from retweet(ed) to reblog(ged)

In order to comply with Twitter 'Developer Display Requirements', we
will use alternative (Twitter's proprietary) terms 'tweet' and 'retweet'
in Twitter accounts and messages ('tweets').
English and Russian language files updated

English and Russian translations updated. Initial help screens are
scrollable now and compatible with Android 4.2

Application Help screens rearranged and are accessible
through Preferences-'About AndStatus' menu. Change Log is also
accessible locally via Preferences-'Change Log'.

1. Swipe gestures added to turn Help pages (HelpActivity)
2. Fixed task 24: Display microblogging service name in the 'Select an
account' button  http://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/issues/issue/24
